in 1569 , ōmura granted a permit for the establishment of a port with the purpose of harboring portuguese ships in nagasaki , which was finally set up in 1571 , under the supervision of the jesuit missionary gaspar vilela and portuguese captain - major tristão vaz de veiga , with ōmura 's personal assistance .

islands : the most southerly of japan 's 4 main islands , it 's where nagasaki is located

